summary: An ordinance authorizing the dismissal of suit instituted by the City of Seattle for condemnation, appropriation, taking of land and other property around Swan Lake et al, for reservoir and pipe line purposes, as provided in Ordinance No. 37022, Cause No. 121648 of the Superior Court of King County, insofar as the same affects certain property in the Northeast quarter of Section 12, Township 22 North, Range 5 East, W.M., Southeast quarter of Section 5, Township 23 North, Range 4 East, W.M., and the Southeast quarter of Section 31, Township 24 North, Range 4 East, W.M., and appropriating money from the Water Fund of the City of Seattle to pay all taxable costs.
